_sText:
This is my first Climb-Map, generally based on a Canyon-Theme. I tried to make a good waterfall, but there is no realistic water-texture for it. :-|

Features: 
- Many easy/normal jumps from 100-200 Units length.
- A Few jumps with more than 200 Units length, which are still possible to pass for "normal"-climbers.
- 2-3 Jumps where you will get in rage. :-O
